body:
### Welcome to Test PROOF.
This automatic page generator is the easiest way to create beautiful pages for all of your projects. Author your page content here [TestRepo03 Example](https://kraka09.github.io/TestRepo03/d/example.html), select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, you can check out the new `gh-pages` branch locally. If you’re using GitHub Desktop, simply sync your repository and you’ll see the new branch.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
